descriptionHtml:
Sacred Grove

*A mod that im currently working on. Looks really nice so far but if anyone wants to help me out on ANYTHING let me know. Im new to the community an would like to make a BIG impact. I believe I have a creative mind and would like to create interesting mods in the future. So please try this an let me know what you think!

___________
*Location 

-West of Whiterun, Its on your map XD
__________
*Features

-Player House and GREAT view of flying dragon. (no load doors)
-Allied with the Boiche guard. (Wood elf guards) *Very Lore Friendly!
-Really nice scenery
-Big trees and misty forest
-A blacksmith
---Just the \"exoskeleton\" as of now. MORE TO COME!!
__________
* Instillation
-Unpack
-Add to data folder
__________
***************
IF YOU WOULD LIKE TO HELP ON THIS PROJECT
PM ME PLEASE. I WOULD LIKE TO SEE THIS MOD 
FLOURISH!
**************
__________

Thank You!
